Step 1/5: Select a business type

Select a business type

You can use the Business Type filter to find out more about different business types.

You can also see what rules and restrictions apply to your chosen business type.

Select your business type

What type of business do you run?

You can select more than one option.

For example, if you run a shop that sells food and drinks, select 'Food and drink shop' and 'Cafe or coffee shop'.

Select your business type

What type of business do you run?

You can select more than one option.

For example, if you run a shop that sells food and drinks, select 'Food and drink shop' and 'Cafe or coffee shop'.

